(firstQuint)Phase II Study With Hiltonol and Dendritic Cells in Solid Tumors.

 In this phase II study, patients with solid tumors will receive treatment with intratumoral hiltonol and two cycles of autologous dendritic cells loaded with autologous tumor and administered subcutaneously.

 A new cohort will explore the role of radiation therapy, looking for an abscopal effect.

